    FROM connected c
    JOIN atom a1 ON c.column_0 = a1.column_0
    JOIN atom a2 ON c.column_1 = a2.column_0
    JOIN bond b ON c.column_2 = b.column_0

    FROM bond_combinations

WITH customer_consumption AS (
    SELECT 
        ym.column_1 AS year_month,
        c.column_0 AS customer_id,
        SUM(t.column_8) AS total_consumption_czk
    FROM 
        transactions_1k t
    JOIN 
        customers c ON t.column_2 = c.column_1
    JOIN 
        yearmonth ym ON c.column_0 = ym.column_0
    WHERE 
        ym.year_month LIKE '2013-%'
    GROUP BY 
        ym.column_1, c.column_0
),
customer_sums AS (
    SELECT 
        customer_id,
        SUM(total_consumption_czk) AS total_annual_consumption
    FROM 
        customer_consumption
    WHERE 
        year_month LIKE '2013-%'
    GROUP BY 
        customer_id
)
SELECT 
    (SUM(CASE WHEN segment = 'SME' THEN total_annual_consumption ELSE 0 END) - SUM(CASE WHEN segment = 'LAM' THEN total_annual_consumption ELSE 0 END)) AS sme_lam_diff,
    (SUM(CASE WHEN segment = 'LAM' THEN total_annual_consumption ELSE 0 END) - SUM(CASE WHEN segment = 'KAM' THEN total_annual_consumption ELSE 0 END)) AS lam_kam_diff,
    (SUM(CASE WHEN segment = 'KAM' THEN total_annual_consumption ELSE 0 END) - SUM(CASE WHEN segment = 'SME' THEN total_annual_consumption ELSE 0 END)) AS kam_sme_diff
FROM 
    (
        SELECT 
            cs.customer_id, 
            p.column_1 AS segment, 
            cs.total_annual_consumption
        FROM 
            customer_sums cs
        JOIN 
            customers c ON cs.customer_id = c.column_0
        JOIN 
            products p ON c.column_2 = p.column_0
    ) subquery
WHERE 
    EXISTS (
        SELECT 1 
        FROM customers c2 
        WHERE c2.column_0 = subquery.customer_id AND c2.column_2 IN ('SME', 'LAM', 'KAM')
    )
GROUP BY 
    subquery.segment
ORDER BY 
    subquery.total_annual_consumption ASC
LIMIT 1;
